data.title: Jeff Donnell - Autograph Note Signed
data.meta_description: Jeff Donnell - Autograph Note Signed  - Item 342147. The popular television actress wishes fan 'much happieness', signs name in blue inkAutograph note signed: 'For Clint -/ Much happiness!/ Jeff Donnell' in blue ink. 5x3 index card. Jean Marie 'Jeff' Donnell (1921-1988) made her film debut in 1942's My Sister Eileen. Shop for  Jeff Donnell related autographs, signed photographs, historical documents and manuscripts from the world's largest collection. Every purchase includes our industry recognized COA. Worldwide shipping available.
